  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;for the Climate Policy Lab&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;The Climate Policy Lab (CPL) will examine mitigation policies (mostly in the developing world) through the lenses of what works, what doesn&#x2019;t and why. The goal is to support the design and implementation of low cost, scalable mitigation solutions that facilitate countries achieving their Nationally Determined Contributions (NDCs) under the Paris Agreement. This will be particularly critical as the U.S. reduces support for such efforts; without U.S. aid, many nations will not have the resources or expertise to meet their commitments. The lab will serve as a resource center for developing nations on policy design and evaluation that is tailored to the local context.&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
